<p>\(z \rightarrow \infty\)ã§2ã¤ã®ç‰©ç†é‡ã¯æ¸›è¡°ã™ã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ãªå¢ƒç•Œæ¡ä»¶ã‚’è¨­å®šã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã™ãªã‚ã¡</p>

\[\xi = \xi_0 e^{\kappa z}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ãªå½¢ã‚’ä»®å®šã—ã¦\(\kappa\)ã®å€¤ã‚’æ±‚ã‚ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ã•ã‚‰ã«\(z\)ãŒå¤§ãã„ã¨ã“ã‚ã§ã¯ã»ã¨ã‚“ã©é‡åŠ›\(g\)ã¯ã»ã¼å€¤ãŒå¤‰ã‚ã‚‰ãªã„ã¨è€ƒãˆã¦(WKBè¿‘ä¼¼)</p>

\[\frac{\partial \xi}{\partial z} 
= \kappa \xi 
= D_{\xi \xi} \xi + D_{\xi \eta} \eta\]

<p>ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\begin{align}
&amp;\frac{\partial^2 \xi }{\partial z^2} 
= \kappa^2 \xi
= D_{\xi \xi} \frac{\partial \xi}{\partial z} + D_{\xi \eta} \frac{\partial \eta}{\partial z} 
= D_{\xi \xi} \kappa \xi + D_{\xi \eta} (D_{\eta \xi} \xi+ D_{\eta \eta} \eta)
= D_{\xi \xi} \kappa \xi + D_{\xi \eta} D_{\eta \xi} \xi + D_{\eta \eta} (\kappa \xi - D_{\xi \xi} \xi) \notag \\
&amp;\Longrightarrow \Â 
\kappa^2 -( D_{\xi \xi} + D_{\eta \eta}) \kappa + D_{\xi \xi}D_{\eta \eta} - D_{\xi \eta} D_{\eta \xi} 
= 0 \notag
\end{align}\]

\[\therefore \ \kappa = \frac{D_{\xi \xi}+ D_{\eta \eta} \pm \sqrt{(D_{\xi \xi}+D_{\eta \eta})^2 -4 (D_{\xi \xi}D_{\eta \eta} -D_{\xi \eta} D_{\eta \xi})}}{2}\]

<p>\(\kappa &lt; 0\)ã®ã¨ãªã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ãªè§£ã‚’é¸æŠã™ã‚‹ã®ã§ã€\(\kappa_{-} = \frac{D_{\xi \xi}+ D_{\eta \eta} - \sqrt{(D_{\xi \xi}+D_{\eta \eta})^2 -4 (D_{\xi \xi}D_{\eta \eta} -D_{\xi \eta} D_{\eta \xi})}}{2}\)ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<p>ã¾ãŸ\(z=0\)ã§ã®å¢ƒç•Œæ¡ä»¶ã¨ã—ã¦ã€\(\xi, \eta\)ã®ã©ã¡ã‚‰ã‹ãŒåå¯¾ç§°ã‚’ä»®å®šã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã™ãªã‚ã¡ã€\(z=0\)ã§ã©ã¡ã‚‰ã‹ã®å€¤ãŒ0ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’å¢ƒç•Œæ¡ä»¶ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

